<h2>Coming in modus-themes version 4.2.0</h2>

<p>I consider this a major step forward that fulfils the potential of the
Modus themes.  Expect the new version to be available in the coming
weeks, either built into the latest development target of Emacs or
from GNU ELPA as a standalone package.</p>

